('RT-Counter: Real-Time Text-Guided Open-Vocabulary Object Counting', 'Hao-Yuan Ma, Li Zhang, Zhiwei Zhu, Jie Gao', '2026', 'Text-guided open-vocabulary object counting (TOOC) aims to count objects belonging to the categories specified by natural language descriptions. Although vision-language pre-trained models have been successful applied to TOOC tasks, they still struggle with fine-grained spatial understanding and rea', 'https://arxiv.org/pdf/2606.17561v1', '0', 'arXiv', 'cs.CV', 'Vision Transformer', datetime('now')),
('Multi-Adapter PPO: A Cross-Attention Enhanced Wavelength Selection Framework for LIBS Quantitative Analysis', 'Hao Li, Man Fung Zhuo', '2026', 'Laser-induced breakdown spectroscopy (LIBS) quantitative analysis faces critical challenges in wavelength selection due to high-dimensional spectral data and the fundamental trade-off between prediction accuracy and feature efficiency. This paper presents a novel Multi-Adapter PPO framework that tra', 'https://arxiv.org/pdf/2606.17476v1', '0', 'arXiv', 'cs.LG', 'Self-Attention', datetime('now')),
